# Global Rules
- Architecture: Single monorepo, no Turborepo.
- Core Principle: JSON is the absolute source of truth. Human-readable text is only a preview generated from JSON.
- API Contract: Backend owns the API. Frontend types are generated from FastAPI OpenAPI.
- Environment: Local-first via Docker Compose (`make dev`).
- Database (MVP): SQLite only.